This paper is about distributed training of deep learning models, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of synchronous and asynchronous optimization methods, which are relevant to distributed computing (cs.DC) and distributed systems (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep learning models for computer vision tasks (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
